org.piwik.sdk

Class TrackMe

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.piwik.sdk.TrackMe
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CustomDimensions

    public class TrackMe
extends Object
    This objects represents one query to Piwik. For each event send to Piwik a TrackMe gets created, either explicitly by you or implicitly by the Tracker.

        public TrackMe set(QueryParams key,

        You can set any additional Tracking API Parameters within the SDK. This includes for example the local time (parameters h, m and s). 
         set(QueryParams.HOURS, "10");
 set(QueryParams.MINUTES, "45");
 set(QueryParams.SECONDS, "30");
        Parameters:

        value - value

        tracker instance
